OL,4,BMario Balotelli: Brescia ultras group
OL,5,Bcalls striker 'arrogant'
OL,6, Brescia's Mario Balotelli has been
OL,7, called "arrogant" by the club's ultras
OL,8, group as it defended Verona fans after
OL,9, some racially abused the Italian.
OL,11,FThe striker, 29, kicked the ball into
OL,12,Fthe crowd and threatened to walk off
OL,13,Fthe pitch after being abused in
OL,14,FSunday's 2-1 defeat at Verona.
OL,16,F"We have no doubts Balotelli is to all
OL,17,Fintents Italian - even a Bresciano,"
OL,18,Fread a statement from Brescia ultras.
OL,20,F"But the arrogance that he continually
OL,21,Fgives off is unjustifiable."
